<lb ed="C I" n="0052a00"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead><title>錡雙胡廿人等造像記</title></jhead></juan>
<lb ed="C I" n="0052a00"/><mulu level="1" label="之一　碑陽" type="其他"/><head>之一　碑陽</head>
<div2>
<lb ed="C I" n="0052a01"/><p id="pI01p0052a0101">富平令王承祖　但官錡眾<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">舉</unclear>　平望田安周　邑子錡陽生
<lb ed="C I" n="0052a02"/>　　　　　　　侍者錡石珍　平望錡神裕　邑子錡景略
<lb ed="C I" n="0052a03"/>　　　　　　　　　　　　　但官錡思山　邑子錡神歡
<lb ed="C I" n="0052a04"/>　　　　　　　　　　　　　邑正錡平洛　邑子錡虎略
<lb ed="C I" n="0052a05"/>邑師錡雙胡　　侍者錡舉　　邑正王買興</p>
</div2>
</div1>
<div1>
<lb ed="C I" n="0052b00"/><mulu level="1" label="之二　碑陰" type="其他"/><head>之二　碑陰</head>
<div2>
<lb ed="C I" n="0052b01"/><p id="pI01p0052b0101">典坐錡道&CB00393;
<lb ed="C I" n="0052b02"/>典錄錡承祖　邑子錡馬仁
<lb ed="C I" n="0052b03"/>邑子錡申起　香火錡神敬
<lb ed="C I" n="0052b04"/>典錄錡歡洛</p>
</div2>
</div1>
<div1>
<lb ed="C I" n="0052c00"/><mulu level="1" label="之三　碑側" type="其他"/><head>之三　碑側</head>
<div2>
<lb ed="C I" n="0052c01"/><p id="pI01p0052c0101">□□□□□先<note n="0052001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB03567;＝劫【史】</note><app n="0052001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">劫</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB03567;</rdg></app>以<note n="0052002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30460;＝來【史】</note><app n="0052002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">來</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30460;</rdg></app>。應形化世。靜志靈<note n="0052003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30452;＝淵【史】</note><app n="0052003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">淵</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30452;</rdg></app>。清脩万行。乃運窮通。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">濁</unclear><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">明</unclear>□
<lb ed="C I" n="0052c02"/><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">三</unclear>□□□<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">世</unclear>之常。事<note n="0052004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30453;＝體【史】</note><app n="0052004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">體</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30453;</rdg></app>真極之妙。嘗獲&CB07099;為以自安。控玄範以騰&CB00418;。馳<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">逸</unclear>
<lb ed="C I" n="0052c03"/>万□。人天蒙<note n="0052005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30454;＝慶【史】</note><app n="0052005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">慶</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30454;</rdg></app>。感緣既周。凝神靜<note n="0052006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30351;＝樂【史】</note><app n="0052006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">樂</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30351;</rdg></app>。真容雖遷。像化<note n="0052007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30394;＝彌【史】</note><app n="0052007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">彌</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30394;</rdg></app>振。然今千載之<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">下</unclear>。
<lb ed="C I" n="0052c04"/>合邑廿人等。覺世非常。捨己名珍。為國為家。造石像一軀。彫<note n="0052008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00018;＝剋【史】</note><app n="0052008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">剋</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB00018;</rdg></app><note n="0052009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30459;＝成【史】</note><app n="0052009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">成</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30459;</rdg></app><note n="0052010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30455;＝就【史】</note><app n="0052010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">就</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30455;</rdg></app>。寫真
<lb ed="C I" n="0052c05"/>容<note n="0052011" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB31034;＝止【史】</note><app n="0052011"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">止</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31034;</rdg></app>。應安處路衝。高平<note n="0052012" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30456;＝顯【史】</note><app n="0052012"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">顯</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30456;</rdg></app>唱。討邑恭養。隨時不闕。以是造像功德。上願皇
<lb ed="C I" n="0052c06"/>□陛下紹隆万劫。匡<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">拯</unclear>三寶。千載不隧。下願合邑亡過師尊父母。長志天
<lb ed="C I" n="0052c07"/><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">闕</unclear>。託化紫蓮。栖神万法。<note n="0052013" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">逯＝逮【史】</note><app n="0052013"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">逮</lem><rdg wit="【原】">逯</rdg></app>及合邑。三界六趣。咸同斯<app source="0052005" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">慶</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30454;</rdg></app>。<note n="0052014" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30457;＝業【史】</note><app n="0052014"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">業</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30457;</rdg></app><app source="0052009" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">成</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30459;</rdg></app>真道。
<lb ed="C I" n="0052c08"/>大□神龜三年歲次庚子年四月甲辰<note n="0052015" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30458;＝朔【史】</note><app n="0052015"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">朔</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30458;</rdg></app>八日造訖。</p>
</div2>
